3.3

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color=class))

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, size = class))

警告を出してくれる

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, alpha = class))

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, shape = class))

shapeは6種類まで

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy), color = "blue")

3.3.1 excercise

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color="blue"))

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color="hoge"))

“blue”という定数値でクラス分けしろ、という命令と解釈された、と思ってcolor=1という文字列でない定数を入れてみたら、変なことになった。 color=Tと論理型だと、期待通りの結果。

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color=1))

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy, color=T))

ex.4

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = displ, color=displ))

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x=displ, y=hwy, stroke=ifelse(drv=="f", 3, 1)), shape=21)

strokeは、線の太さを変える

3.5 Facets

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = displ, y = hwy)) +
  facet_wrap(~ class, nrow=2)

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x=displ, y=hwy)) + 
  facet_grid(drv ~ cyl)

facetの軸(drv, cyl)を画面に出す方法を知りたい

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x=displ, y=hwy)) + 
  facet_grid(.~class)

ggplot(data = mpg) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x=displ, y=hwy)) + 
  facet_wrap(~class)

face_gridとfacet_wrapの違い - facet_warp: よしなに並べてくれる - facet_grid: 意地でも一列を保つ

Q: 連続変数でfacetしたら？ A: 大変なことになる

ggplot(data=data.frame(x=1:20, y=rnorm(20))) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x=x, y=y)) +
  facet_wrap(~y)
